Title: Relates to regulating the operation of animal boarding kennels
Summary: Provides for the licensing, inspection and regulation of animal boarding kennels; authorizes the department of agriculture and markets to license, inspect and regulate animal boarding kennels.
LawCode: Add Art 26-D §§440 - 449-b, amd §16, Ag & Mkts L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the agriculture and markets law, in relation to regulating the operation of animal boarding kennels
